
## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.so

# Packaging
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/

# Tool caches
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# IDEs
.vscode/
.idea/

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Runtime artifacts
recordings/*
!recordings/.gitkeep

assets/models/*
!assets/models/.gitkeep

# Local environment files
.env
.env.*